Package edu.cmu.commons.mtj.io

Input/output routines for data types within the Matrix Toolkit for Java (MTJ).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
MatrixReader Reads a compressed row or column (sparse) matrix from an input stream.
MatrixWriter Writes a compressed row or column (sparse) matrix to an output stream.
VectorReader  
VectorWriter  
 

Class Summary
AbstractMatrixReader Base class for MatrixReader implementations.
AbstractMatrixWriter Base class for MatrixWriter implementations.
AbstractVectorReader Base class for VectorReader implementations.
AbstractVectorWriter Base class for VectorWriter implementations.
BinaryMatrixReader MatrixReader supporting binary format.
BinaryMatrixWriter MatrixWriter supporting binary format.
BinaryVectorReader VectorReader supporting binary format.
BinaryVectorWriter VectorWriter supporting binary format.
TextMatrixReader MatrixReader supporting text format.
TextMatrixWriter MatrixWriter supporting text format.
TextVectorReader VectorReader supporting text format.
TextVectorWriter VectorWriter supporting text format.
 

Package edu.cmu.commons.mtj.io Description

Input/output routines for data types within the Matrix Toolkit for Java (MTJ). Tested with MTJ 0.9.9.
